## Session data: dead-field guards, triplestore stats TTL, stamp documentation

### Context

Session optimization: remove defensive pops for legacy keys that nothing writes
anymore; add a time-to-live for ``domain.triplestore`` stats cache (same idea as
``version_status``); document why ``last_update`` / change flags stay persisted.

