   ``_validation_cache`` and ``_document_count``; removed ``import_from_file()``
   pops for ``triplestore.needs_rebuild`` and ``triplestore.build_fingerprint``;
   documented in ``save()`` that ``last_update``, ``ontology_changed``, and
   ``assignment_changed`` are intentionally stored (cheap stamp vs recomputation).
   On project import, ``triplestore`` cache clear now also pops
   ``_ts_cache_timestamp``.

