   ``_TS_STATS_CACHE_TTL_SECONDS`` (300); ``set_ts_cache`` sets
   ``triplestore._ts_cache_timestamp``; ``get_ts_cache`` returns ``None`` when
   the stamp is missing or older than the TTL (aligned with
