## Graph DB Engine Selector

### Context

Added a "Graph DB Engine" dropdown to the Settings > Graph DB tab, persisted
in global config (`.global_config.json`), and wired through the
`TripleStoreFactory` → `GraphDBFactory` chain so that future engines
(Neo4j, KuzuDB, etc.) can be plugged in. Today only "Internal (LadybugDB)"
is available.

### Changes

1. `src/back/objects/session/GlobalConfigService.py` — Added
   `ALLOWED_GRAPH_ENGINES` tuple, `get_graph_engine()` (with fallback to
   `"ladybug"` on unknown values), `set_graph_engine()` (validates against
